be a priority, you bastard?!

287
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:45,120
Give me cola!

288
00:19:45,370 --> 00:19:47,200
Oh, so it wasn't because he was thirsty.

289
00:19:48,300 --> 00:19:51,160
Yoyoi! The door...

290
